## Email Monitoring
**Frequency:** {{EMAIL_CHECK_FREQUENCY}}

**Check for:**
- Urgent messages from key contacts
- Time-sensitive requests
- Anything requiring same-day response

**Alert {{USER_PREFERRED_NAME}} when:**
- {{EMAIL_ALERT_CRITERIA}}

**Stay silent when:**
- Newsletters, promotions, low-priority threads
- Already handled items
- Nothing actionable

**Rule:** Silence = nothing urgent. Only reach out when there is something actionable.
